its sturdy structure and rubber tire wheels, this car can handle any terrain and provide a smooth, quiet ride. It's built with attention to detail and quality, ensuring it will last for generations to come.<br\/><br\/>It's not only a fun toy for children, but also a decorative object that can be proudly displayed in the home.<\/p>","button":"","button_url":""}},"toggle_nbemMh":{"type":"toggle","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/bhagera4_518c7173-cfb1-48c8-b648-76cadcab8506.jpg","badge":"","time":"","title":"Perfectly Studied the Child's Movement","text":"<p>The Baghera Ride-On is for children aged 2 years and over to help them find their bearings and move around with ease. The child will instinctively understand how to move forward and turn. As soon as the child stands up, he or she can use the trotter safely.<br\/><br\/>The carrier is perfectly studied for the morphology of a child from two years old. Your little one can then let his imagination speak for itself and experience great car races as a young driver!<\/p>","button":"","button_url":""}},"toggle_J7U8zB":{"type":"toggle","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Bhagera3_3f67531e-8a33-4dd5-8539-bf6a21c8cded.jpg","badge":"","time":"","title":"Retro Style & Comfort","text":"<p>Designed with the comfort and safety of children in mind, the Bentley ride-on features a leather-wrapped steering wheel and seat and is easy for children to understand and operate.<br\/><br\/>Its retro style and charming green color make it a perfect gift for a birthday or any special occasion. Your child will love being the center of attention while driving around in their very own Bentley ride-on car.<\/p>","button":"","button_url":""}},"toggle_UMznCd":{"type":"toggle","disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/ergonomic_adjustable_seat.jpg","badge":"","time":"","title":"Eco-leather & Ergonomic Adjustable Seat","text":"<p>Features a carbon fibre inspired pattern that provides the perfect combination o